Articles.Content:
So today may not be so important to you, but it was for me. For the first time I have landed 3 kerbals on Duna and returned them alive to Kerbin without cheats. Enjoy.

> [**Javascript is disabled. View full album**](//imgur.com/a/%5B/b%5DmIJk8)

**Here's a direct link if it doesn't work:** [**http://imgur.com/a/mIJk8**](http://imgur.com/a/mIJk8)

Nicely done! ![:D](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif) I still remember how proud I was of my first Duna mission that actually managed to return from the planet. It's certainly an exhilarating feeling, isn't it?
Nice! Duna is a very fun trip. Ike can be fun too, if you meet him on purpose. ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)
Just finishing up my Duna and return of 2 Kerbals mission, was alot of fun. I enjoyed your pictures and comments on your trip as well. Well done!
